<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id0615b586-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d" identifier="/us/usc/t19/s3706"><num value="3706">§ 3706.</num><heading> Sub-Saharan Africa defined</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">For purposes of this chapter, the terms “sub-Saharan Africa”, “sub-Saharan African country”, “country in sub-Saharan Africa”, and “countries in sub-Saharan Africa” refer to the following or any successor political entities:</p>
